      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Jun 2021 11:15:20 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://carakan.net/blog/2021/06/dropbox-ignore-files-directories/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Ignoring files or directories in dropbox is a hard thing, I thought it has like git,
a &lt;code&gt;.gitignore&lt;/code&gt; to config that, but no, we need to do a command for each file/dir, for example to ignore
the files that creates a lightroom catalog (.lrcat) we need to do:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;xattr -w com.dropbox.ignored &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; /Users/username/Dropbox/lightroom/2021-v10&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\ &lt;/span&gt;Previews.lrdata
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;xattr -w com.dropbox.ignored &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; /Users/username/Dropbox/lightroom/2021-v10&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\ &lt;/span&gt;Previews.lrdata
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;xattr -w com.dropbox.ignored &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; /Users/username/Dropbox/lightroom/2021-v10&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\ &lt;/span&gt;Helper.lrdata
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;and to not longer ignore files we need this command:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Make Backup/Restore Postgres Database With No Owner</title>
      <link>https://carakan.net/blog/2021/02/make-backup/restore-postgres-database-with-no-owner/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Feb 2021 17:01:57 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://carakan.net/blog/2021/02/make-backup/restore-postgres-database-with-no-owner/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;to do backup:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;pg_dump dbname -O -x &amp;gt; backupname.sql
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;To restore:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;psql dbname &amp;lt; backupname.sql
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Options documentation:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-txt&#34; data-lang=&#34;txt&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;-O &amp;lt;-- No owner
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;-x &amp;lt;-- No privileges
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
