    <item>
      <title>Upgrade to Latest Version on ASDF</title>
      <link>https://carakan.net/blog/2019/09/upgrade-to-latest-version-on-asdf/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2019 10:44:57 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://carakan.net/blog/2019/09/upgrade-to-latest-version-on-asdf/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;ASDF is an incredible version manager, to install/upgrade to latest version available
of an language you can do the following steps:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;asdf list-all &amp;lt;language&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;this show all of the versions available to install, select the latest:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;asdf install &amp;lt;language&amp;gt; x.y.z
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;and edit if you have a global &lt;code&gt;~/.tool-versions&lt;/code&gt; to use that version everywhere:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-txt&#34; data-lang=&#34;txt&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lt;languaje&amp;gt; x.y.z
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;real-example&#34;&gt;real example&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;to upgrade to latest version of erlang &lt;strong&gt;(10/17/2019)&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;asdf list-all erlang
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;asdf install erlang 22.1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;asdf global erlang 22.1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Enable Prettier in Ember templates</title>
